org.hackystat.sensor.eclipse.addon
Class JavaStructureChangeDetector

java.lang.Object
  org.hackystat.sensor.eclipse.addon.JavaStructureChangeDetector

public class JavaStructureChangeDetector
extends java.lang.Object

Listens to the java element change events to get incremental work on java objects and collect refactoring information for test-driven development analysis purpose. It's declared as package private so that it can only be instantiated by Eclise sensor.
